name: Jetfuelvision
tagline: They say data is jet fuel. We're the jet.
body:
### About
We are a SAAS company that provides state of the art data processing techniques for time series data by building on the shoulders of giants. Our backbone is powered by deep learning neural networks especially designed for time series data. This deep learning model helped AlphaGo defeat Lee Sedol 4-1 last spring <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AlphaGo_versus_Lee_Sedol>.

Our speech APIs enable you to analyze your speech data and get a demographic profile from the voice data (of course, you also get structured data about the message itself). We know your time is valuable, so our APIs are designed for low latency and high throughput. You can hit us with all you've got.

Stay tuned for our prediction API set.

Currently, we are no longer accepting additional customers for our beta. 

For inquiries, please reach out to jetfuelvision@gmail.com  
If you have an issue with our APIs, please include "BETA SUPPORT: " in the subject line.
